Description: Located in Olney, a suburban town on the edge of countryside, situated between Washington DC and Baltimore, this 4 bed/2.5 bath end unit town home is in the ideal location. Featuring hardwood floors, ceiling fans, and a desirable color scheme, it offers plenty of storage space and built in shelving units. Master suite includes walk-in closet and attached bathroom. Finished walk-out basement leads to fenced backyard with patio. Backs up to Cherrywood Park. Short drive to Olney Town Center for shopping and dining options. Close to 97 (Georgia Ave) and 200 (The ICC). Reserved/guest parking available. No pets.

One Time Fees:
* Application Fee: $25
* Cat Deposit: $300
* Dog Deposit: $300
Pet Policy:
Dogs Allowed:
Cats and dogs are welcome. Maximum two pets per apartment. Monthly fees: $20 per cat, $30 per dog. Refundable deposit: $300 (first pet only). Breed restrictions and other limitations apply. No weight limit.

* 200 lb Weight Limit
* 2 Pet Limit

Description: Tamarron Apartments is the only apartment community in the charming town of Olney, MD. These one-, two-, and three-bedroom apartments for rent have it all dual-entry gourmet kitchens with separate dining room, washer/dryer, walk-in closets, balcony or patio, stylish finishes, and off-street parking. You'll also enjoy our tennis courts, swimming pool, clubhouse, soccer/baseball field and a 2.3-acre lake with walking paths. * Located off Georgia Avenue, with easy access to Silver Spring, Rockville, and the DC area, Tamarron Apartments is close to Montgomery General Hospital, shopping and live theater. Hop on I-95, I-97, I-270 or U.S. Route 29, Route 32, and Route 108, and you'll be to your destination in no time! The bus stop, Glenmont Metro and Wheaton Metro are nearby, too. Bring your cat or dog along pets are welcome and there's no weight limit! If you'd like to learn more, Tamarron Apartments has a bilingual staff to answer any questions you may have.
